snippet.title: Eternal Paradox | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Eternal Paradox is an upcoming Web3 4X RPG adventure created by NDream and brought to you by Gala Games.

Build alliances, collect resources, customize Mercenaries and save the world from ruin, all while owning your experience and earning real rewards.

Eternal Paradox
https://eternal-paradox.game/

Join the discussion in Discord:
http://galagames.chat/
